title: Cadorabo Case Compatible with Apple iPhone 6 / iPhone 6S in Pastel Purple - Shockproof and Scratch Resistant TPU Silicone Cover - Ultra Slim Protective Gel Shell Bumper Back Skin
features: DESIGN: Only 1.2 mm thick so it offers an almost unchanged appearance of your Smartphone. It doesn´t matter which color you´ll choose, your phone is well protected but still does not cover any important details of your smartphone. The TPU Silicone case clings perfectly to your phone and remains elastic and stable in form at once and therefore it is hardly noticeable. FUNCTION: All ports and buttons are accessible without restriction (camera / headset etc.) There is no annoying flap and no nonfunctional case. The surface is roughened, and non-slippery. Although the material is thin, light and soft, the phone shell provides excellent bumper shock absorption. The phone reception is not affected by this cover.

QUALITY: Only flexible TPU material was used for the manufacture. This transparent material (TPU / silicone) was chosen to provide durability and stability. The soft, flexible and slim silicone case prevents air to be trapped between the cover and your smartphone. with regard to the processing everything was taken into account: clean cutouts, no entrapped air, slim material and firm grip.

PROTECTION: The cell phone case protects every corner and edge of your Smartphone. The case covers the entire backside of your phone (except for the camera and other important features). The edges of this cover are raised by 0.5 mm which provides additional protection for your screen. Thanks to the used TPU / silicone hybrid material this soft material cover offers perfect shock absorption compared to a hard cover case. This means stylish as well as secure covering for your mobile phone.

ADDITIONAL INFORMATION: In spite of the good protection, we recommend to apply a protective film for the display. This provides extra protection against scratches the screen and can be purchased in our store as well. The Smartphone shown is not included in delivery.
